rs at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using the premium index between perpetual and spot prices. Long positions pay shorts when rates are positive, with payments occurring automatically at funding timestamps. The zero maker fee structure allows traders to build positions cost-effectively, though the 0.03% taker fee applies to market orders."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
